name: Angel of Death
description:
I imagined the angel of death not like Grim Reaper. I imagined He a mix betwen paradise and hell. And this the simple story about the Angel of death:


He just away from hell, maybe he want refreshing his daily from work pressure. And then, his cell phone ringing. He take phone, and see one message. That message from the boss, he must find one soul to his boss. Now, he not off work anymore. haha...
